      "writtenOn": "2018-06-05T20:40:46Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Why do you need a NewGlobalRef? Does this get called by another native method? If this returns to Java, I think you\u0027re safe to just return \"array\". If this does create a Global Ref, I think it should be documented. (Also, who deletes it?)",
